    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047910/extras/d115b9d429f24343299481df4578468b.poster.avif?t=1759837033\" width=652 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047910/extras/d115b9d429f24343299481df4578468b.webm?t=1759837033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047910/extras/d115b9d429f24343299481df4578468b.mp4?t=1759837033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You were just minding your business when suddenly, a bunch of portals opened up all over the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just like many other ducks, you fell into the portal and were left stranded in another world. But a lone duck traversed the portals and saved you and everyone else.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now, inspired by the actions of the previous hero, you've joined the Exploration Guild, whose purpose is to chart and explore other worlds. Your expeditions are powered by the Power Crystal, an other worldly gem capable of producing portals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But soon, you'll find that its use has unintended consequences....</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047910/extras/afbc96b98605fc78b4f189ceb4709eab.poster.avif?t=1759837033\" width=652 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047910/extras/afbc96b98605fc78b4f189ceb4709eab.webm?t=1759837033\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3047910/extras/afbc96b98605fc78b4f189ceb4709eab.mp4?t=1759837033\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use water-powered flight to navigate the world</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Maintain your momentum and master the controls</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a set of challenging levels across different worlds</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 chapters</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level editor, player levels</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leaderboards</p></li></ul>",
